Edward Atienza https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Atienza 0 Edward Atienza (27 January 1924 – 16 September 2014) was a British stage and film actor. He made his first London theatre appearance in the role of Mole in Toad of Toad Hall at the Prince's Theatre.
